msgid "Contact"
msgstr "Contact"

msgid "The smarter way to study"
msgstr "La facon la plus intelligente d'etudier"

msgid "Master any subject"
msgstr "Maitrisez n'importe quelle matiere"

msgid "at your own pace"
msgstr "a votre rythme"

msgid "Create custom word lists with flexible study fields. Study with flashcards,"
msgstr "Creez des listes personnalisees avec des champs flexibles. Etudiez avec des flashcards,"

msgid "track your progress, and actually remember what you learn."
msgstr "suivez vos progres et retenez vraiment ce que vous apprenez."

msgid "Start for free"
msgstr "Commencez gratuitement"

msgid "Definition"
msgstr "Definition"

msgid "Lasting for a very short time"
