msgid "The ephemeral beauty of cherry blossoms"
msgstr "La beaute ephemere des fleurs de cerisier"

msgid "Everything you need to study effectively"
msgstr "Tout ce dont vous avez besoin pour etudier efficacement"

msgid "Custom Study Lists"
msgstr "Listes d'etude personnalisees"

msgid "Create word lists tailored to any subject — vocabulary, formulas, dates, concepts."
msgstr "Creez des listes adaptees a chaque sujet — vocabulaire, formules, dates, concepts."

msgid "Flexible Fields"
msgstr "Champs flexibles"

msgid "Add as many fields as you need per word: description, examples, notes, and more."
msgstr "Ajoutez autant de champs que necessaire: description, exemples, notes, et plus."

msgid "Fast & Simple"
msgstr "Rapide et simple"

msgid "A clean interface that gets out of your way so you can focus on learning."
msgstr "Une interface claire qui vous laisse vous concentrer sur l'apprentissage."

msgid "Have a question or feedback? We would love to hear from you."
msgstr "Une question ou un retour? Nous serions ravis de vous lire."

msgid "We usually reply within 24 hours."
msgstr "Nous repondons generalement sous 24 heures."

